{"tid":2295583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：強制檢測基層或卻步　確診者可獲5千元津貼","createTime":"2020-11-22T02:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T09:08:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"beb519233e5f416bd9da5ff939c238f7b71d5764","tid":2295583,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:01:16.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，本地新型肺炎疫情已惡化，當局要強化檢測工作，今日亦針對「跳舞群組」發出指示，要求本月1日至21日到過14間指明跳舞場所的人士，要在24日或之前接受檢測。她又說，部分人尤其基層市民對強制檢測可能會卻步，了解到有些人擔心確診後會影響生計，當局會向確診者發放一筆過5000元津貼，勞工及福利局敲定細節後會盡快公布。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始在一個電台節目說，要強制檢測的人士假如沒有在指示日期前檢測，可被罰款或檢控，當局設立強制檢測並不是想懲罰人，而是希望有關人士接受檢測，幫忙遏止疫情。她說，當局亦計劃再增加最少5個社區檢測中心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561276-20201122.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561276-20201122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=9575b68f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561276-20201122.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=28b6e856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561276-20201122.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d48b8dfdcd5b87ca7e1572905638f7669c7d5c47","tid":2295583,"uid":99883,"like":137,"dislike":2,"score":135,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"有錢攞，大把廢老即刻罩都唔戴搏仲招，起碼有5千銀落袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85186f993e2a701c73ceac69e7e1ef3cb3c52049","tid":2295583,"uid":343712,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"弱智都未必諗到嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa3a40d5773746ba4d9d44ec9f5a269a780c012","tid":2295583,"uid":19842,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T02:06:01.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\nd人會更加放肆去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"